  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "textHash": "e3c3a7c619c6516bffb52baf6d44439feae6d9979626453df6c197986213b738",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-fork-isolation/intro.e3c3a7c6.mp3",
      "narrationText": "欢迎回来！上次你见识了 fork 命令。现在来看看它们究竟意味着什么：一个实时运行的数据库应用，几秒内完成复制，可以随意编辑，而原版完全感知不到任何变化。",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.804082
    },
    {
      "id": "what-is-a-fork",
      "textHash": "e0b6cf5ffcd8dc06910c0a88c20cb6eed13e8a6dc63410ee58e433e34c256f29",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-fork-isolation/what-is-a-fork.e0b6cf5f.mp3",
      "narrationText": "先说背景：一个真实的 PostgreSQL，上面挂着 pgAdmin 界面，在服务器上实时运行。fork 是对整个环境的即时写时复制副本。诞生时数据完全相同，之后各自独立运行。",
      "audioDurationSec": 19.565714
    },
    {
      "id": "grand-pgadmin",
      "textHash": "f7f40f12be2180321c1b038db46ccd2b06ba9f1c728f1eb9a9df7e46c88c9801",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-fork-isolation/grand-pgadmin.f7f40f12.mp3",
      "narrationText": "这是原版，在浏览器里打开。pgAdmin 要求登录，因为这是生产环境的副本，生产环境始终受到保护。",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.515918
    },
    {
      "id": "fork-pgadmin",
      "textHash": "3dfbb1d63e7857021f949ac0a83d19a79d0507ab731a875bc41c2c976b8bbe6a",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-fork-isolation/fork-pgadmin.3dfbb1d6.mp3",
      "narrationText": "这是 fork 的 pgAdmin。这次不需要登录，fork 是一次性的 sandbox，所以门卫直接让路。表相同，数据行相同，但它有自己独立的世界。",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.930612
    },
    {
      "id": "side-by-side",
      "textHash": "50a22129a50d130cd929b0a08709bb9dd642ad8c3229ad498780eeaf48521700",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-fork-isolation/side-by-side.50a22129.mp3",
      "narrationText": "现在并排对比：左边是 fork，右边是原版。在左边随意编辑、删除、搞破坏，右边纹丝不动。这就是看得见的隔离效果。",
      "audioDurationSec": 11.467755
    },
    {
      "id": "next-tutorial",
      "textHash": "f996535f2b3e357ee69a7124596dc11ab643ddb25459998047ab56cad4c0c591",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-fork-isolation/next-tutorial.f996535f.mp3",
      "narrationText": "所以尽管随意 fork，生产环境不会受到任何影响。下一期，我们来看 secrets，也就是 fork 刻意不继承的那一样东西。到时见！",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.355918
    }
  ]
}
